  "ai_usage": "Use as a personal/creative portfolio scaffold. Copy the document, set the three color tokens, and replace the name/role, the project cards (title, category, link, and the placeholder thumbnail), the about paragraph, and the contact email. The project grid is auto-fit responsive. Keep it sparse — the design relies on whitespace and type scale. Swap placeholder gradients for real <img> with alt text.",
